# Gemini Image Generation Skill

This project includes a custom skill for generating AI images using Google Gemini API.

## When to Use

Use this skill when the user asks to:
- Create or generate images
- Generate artwork or illustrations
- Create images in specific styles (Ghibli, Pixar, Cyberpunk, etc.)
- Generate concept art or visual designs
- Create variations of an image concept

## How to Use

Read the skill file at `.cursor/skills/gemini-image-gen/SKILL.md` for complete instructions.

## Quick Reference

### Single Image Generation
```bash
python scripts/generate_image.py "A magical forest" --style ghibli
```

### Batch Generation
```bash
python scripts/batch_generate.py "A cute robot" --count 4 --style pixar
```

## Available Styles

| Style | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| ghibli | Studio Ghibli anime style |
| pixar | Pixar 3D animation style |
| cyberpunk | Neon-lit cyberpunk aesthetic |
| chinese-painting | Traditional Chinese ink painting |
| oil-painting | Classical oil painting |
| watercolor | Soft watercolor style |
| anime | Modern anime style |
| fantasy | Epic fantasy art |

## Requirements

- `GEMINI_API_KEY` environment variable must be set
- Dependencies: `pip install google-genai pillow`
